name: Hopful woman
description: In the hustle and bustle of this city, amidst the hustle and bustle of people who have forgotten the meaning of life, I saw a woman full of eagerness to be free, tired of running and not reaching; The dancers wandered the back alleys of the city in search of some street light. He believed that the black heart would one day blossom with a glimmer of hope from the pain of the people.
